		"Details": "A purely experimental weapons platform, the Hyperion Superheavy BattleMech was designed in concert by a number of members of various Clan scientist castes. Somehow, using the cutting edge science available to them, the Clan scientists managed to produce a viable superheavy chassis, the first since the Matar centuries before. After extensive testing, the Clans decided to develop the Hyperion as an OmniMech capable of matching, if not exceeding the famous Dire Wolf in speed, armor, and firepower. Built on a 375-rated XL engine, with an Endo-Steel Framework with 18.5 tons of Ferro-Fibrous armor, the Hyperion Omni boasts a staggering 72.5 tons of free tonnage for weaponry and equipment. In its stock configuration, the Prime mounts two of the largest weapons in the Clan arsenal: the HAG 40. Ten tons of ammunition ensure that the Mech can keep firing, and four ER Large Lasers give the Prime an impressive long range punch. \n\n <b><color=#e51717>COMMUNITY CONTENT</color></b>",
